          <p class="t-body-large">
            I am a <span class="about-badge">Physician & Clinical Data Analyst</span> (known as <strong>Blue</strong>) and a Travel Medicine Resident at the Institute of Preventive Medicine, Thailand. I specialize in bridging clinical practice with data architecture, having completed a <a href="https://digihealth.md.chula.ac.th/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Master of Science in Digital and AI Technologies in Health Systems</a> at Chulalongkorn University and starting a <a href="https://www.heinz.cmu.edu/programs/health-care-analytics-master/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Master of Science in Health Care Analytics and Information Technology</a> at Carnegie Mellon University’s Heinz College of Information Systems and Public Policy in 2026.
          </p>
          <p class="t-body-large font-mono" style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:var(--accent-heading);margin-top:1.25rem;" hidden>
